column5: Have you heard the one:  Q. Why do women fake it?  A. Because they think men care.   Well it seems that female brown trout get the last laugh at that one.   http://www.bbc.com/earth/story/20150214-fake-orgasms-and-other-sex-lies
the one that made me laugh was the green and black poison dart frog  and the one on the  topi antelope is good also
